1.3
log
@nuke "unused" warnings appearing on -Wall
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: ls.c,v 1.20 2003/06/11 23:42:12 deraadt Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: ls.c,v 1.18 1996/07/09 09:16:29 mycroft Exp $	*/

